[{"id":"VH906194","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">If <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"N a\"><math alttext=\"N a\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Na</mtext><mtext></mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> reacts with chlorine to form <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"N a C l\"><math alttext=\"N a C l\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>NaCl</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, which of the following elements reacts with <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"N a\"><math alttext=\"N a\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Na</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> to form an ionic compound in a one-to-one ratio, and why?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH906194_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K\"><math alttext=\"K\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>K</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, because it is in the same group as <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"N a\"><math alttext=\"N a\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Na</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"M g\"><math alttext=\"M g\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Mg</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, because its mass is similar to that of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"N a\"><math alttext=\"N a\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Na</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A r\"><math alttext=\"A r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Ar</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, because its mass is similar to that of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C l\"><math alttext=\"C l\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Cl</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B r\"><math alttext=\"B r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Br</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, because it has the same number of valence electrons as <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C l\"><math alttext=\"C l\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Cl</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>"],"answer":3}]